title: ’Canes go south against North

’Canes go south against North By Danny Daniels   
MONROE — North Oconee spoiled homecoming for Monroe Area Friday night, beating the Purple Hurricanes 33-6. 
The Titans held their hosts to eight first downs and 10 rushing yards.
